rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0001
rows.name:
Now the question is, how are we
getting to the Cliffs of Mors?

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0002
rows.name:
I doubt just any sailor would be
willing to give us a ride there.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0003
rows.name:
Yeah, they're not gonna be keen on
going that close to the World Tree.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0004
rows.name:
In that case, I will charter a
military vessel.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0005
rows.name:
It may not be the most efficient
route, but it will be reliable, I can
assure you that much.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0008
rows.name:
Haha... Some might consider this an
abuse of my privileges, you know.

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0009
rows.name:
So are we headed to the port at
Hadashal Palace in Superbia?

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0011
rows.name:
Kagutsuchi, would you send word ahead
that we are coming?

rows.label: fev07_410_160_msg0012
rows.name:
Of course, Meleph-sama.
Leave it to me.
